New in version 0.7.1 (August 2010) :
- Fixed crashes/memory leaks
- Fixed door code
- Proper build script for GNU-based systems

New in version 0.7.0 (July 2010) :
(This new version restores many features that were broken in previous
version and fixes 2 big bugs)
- ** Fix badly bugged collision system (GNU "standard method" builds) **
- ** Fix bad crash when user quits (GNU "standard method" builds) **
- ** Player can jump properly even at low health (old weird mistake fixed) **
- ** PowerBar now properly fades out **
- ** Door teleport animation (fade in/out) restored ! **
- Cleaned code a little
- Less useless old 'debug' messages

New in version 0.6.9 (April 2010) :

- Common source for Mac OS X/Windows/Unix/Mac OS 9
- Background multiplane scrolling fixed
- Better packaging
- Windows build has icon & program info
